fields.name: EnableIPv6
fields.description: Indicates wether to enable Ipv6 or not. If not provided, it will take the same configuration as the cluster.

fields.name: NetworkSecurityGroupId
fields.description: Full resource id for the network security group.

fields.name: PrivateEndpointNetworkPolicies
fields.description: Enable or Disable apply network policies on private end point in the subnet.

fields.name: PrivateLinkServiceNetworkPolicies
fields.description: Enable or Disable apply network policies on private link service in the subnet.
